      <h2>Hello!</h2>

      <p>My name is Isabelle, and I am the founder and editor of The Traveling Times. This site is my creative journal — a place where I write about all the things I love and find interesting.</p>

      <p>I cover travel, poetry, entertainment, fashion, art, music, and dance. Sometimes I write about one of these things, and sometimes I mix them all together. There are no rules here except to be curious and have fun.</p>

      <h2>Why The Traveling Times?</h2>

      <p>I started this site because I wanted a place to share my adventures, my ideas, and the things that inspire me. Whether it is a poem I wrote on a rainy afternoon, a dance performance that gave me chills, or a city I have always wanted to visit, this is where it all lives.</p>

      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>

      <p>Have a question, a comment, or just want to say hi? You can reach me at <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a>.</p>

